{"tid":676414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金仔棄核】外國記者團見證 北韓炸毀坑道拆除核試場","createTime":"2018-05-24T10:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T16:05:03.000Z","uid":18348,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e47a62fd34abb5673fb423fe71a43d131ea60386","tid":676414,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:44:38.000Z","msg":"北韓周四正式開始拆除吉州豐溪里核試驗場，獲准採訪的外國記者在現場直擊拆除過程，韓聯社報道指，北韓已炸毀了核試場內的坑道。<br />\n<br />\n核試驗場所在地咸鏡北道地區早前下雨，北韓官員昨天曾對南韓記者表示，如果今天的天氣良好，便會開始拆除試驗場。<br />\n<br />\n吉州豐溪里核試驗場共有4條坑道，首兩條坑道在早前的核試後已關閉或因倒塌而棄用，現餘第3號及第4號坑道。來自南韓等5個國家的外國記者團可有望見証北韓爆破核坑道，但觀看的位置則還未公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180524&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58233009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180524%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58233009&d=J2oGmjc0TVxNz9Yc%2BhJ3cv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=ca583d57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180524%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58233009&h=e6166760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180524&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58233009</a>"},{"pid":"4b4e92441acc7da344f8e48326c1782831abc9e6","tid":676414,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:57:29.000Z","msg":"5毛呢？"},{"pid":"2bb84f8cb2bed5e3aa5f99c3ea90edf8ab4f91b3","tid":676414,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"真係拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a001cda617c8cce9519deb2d7c5c30eb80cd8c","tid":676414,"uid":2230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bb84f8cb2bed5e3aa5f99c3ea90edf8ab4f91b3","tid":676414,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:58:15.000Z","msg":"真係拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i